Pantron got the message from phobia. He locked on to the coordinates and took his leave. He took the order not to use his comm. He arrived at the coordinates unsure weither Phbia would be waiting for him.
  cyberwolf4@... wrote: 
Phobia knew about Pantron, he'd heard enough to know that neither one 
of them could step anywhere within 100 miles of Magmatrons base 
without a eulogy handy. Phobia had deceived and swindled the 
Destrucon leader and he knew one day he'd have slag to pay. Unless he 
had a scape goat, or at least a scape panther to take the blow for 
him. On this planet he needed all the shields he could find.

Phobia to Pantor, if you're familiar with the Destrucon map of this 
planet meet me at coordinates 9211-8 (What will one day be southern 
Japan.) If youcan arrange transportation. Keep radio silence from 
here on out.

After broadcasting the message to Pantor, he set communications to a 
group of Predicons he'd detected near the Arks location. With the 
press of a button he repeated the comunication to them.

(Megatron, Hellbeast, this means you.)
